Label: Complex

Label: Complex
Comment: cRNA bound by NP and trimeric polymerase, capable of vRNA synthesis from the cRNA template.

Label: Viral Polymerase
Comment: Heterotrimeric influenza viral polymerase complex consisting of PB1, PB2, and PA;  although capable of being imported into the nucleus independently, the three subunits of the influenza polymerase assemble in the nucleus to form a mature ternary polymerase complex that binds viral vRNA or cRNA (reviewed in Buolo et al., 2006).
